ATHENS , May 29 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- Greece Friday expressed its opposition to the use of nuclear weapons .
Commenting on the nuclear tests conducted by Pakistan , Greek government spokesman Dimitris Reppas told reporters here that Greece was opposed to the use of weapons and more so to the use of nuclear weapons .
In a related development , a group of 20 members of the environmental organization Greenpeace Friday demonstrated outside the Pakistani embassy in Athens to protest Thursday 's five nuclear tests carried out by Pakistan in response to the testing two weeks ago by India of five nuclear devices .
